◆ SelectMany< TIn, TOut >() [1/2]

static IProducer<TOut> Microsoft.Psi.Operators.SelectMany< TIn, TOut > ( this IProducer< TIn >  source,
Func< TIn, Envelope, IEnumerable< TOut >>  selector,
DeliveryPolicy  policy = null 
)
static

Executes a function for each item in the input stream, generating a new stream with the (zero or more) values returned by the function. The function must return an IEnumerable<TOut>, which can be System.Linq.Enumerable.Empty<TOut> to indicate zero results. The values in the returned IEnumerable<TOut> are emitted as separate messages with the same oringinating time.

Template Parameters
TInThe input message type
TOutThe output message type
Parameters

selectorThe function to perform on every message in the source stream. The function has access to the envelope of the input message.
policyAn optional delivery policy
Returns
A stream of type TOut
